responses: {"Q0":"It was simple, but I think that can make it an effective way to find simple trends.","Q1":"I checked each box for punishment and rewards, and then found the green box kept rewarding me, until I used it too many times. So in-between green choices I chose the purple box because it would not really penalise me (+50-50) and my progress would remain the same. I got more cautious as I neared the end, and mixed up my choices slightly more frequently."}
